      "Games and NFTs": "ゲームとNFT",
      "Decentralized prediction markets, such as Augur and Gnosis, use the wisdom of the crowd to predict real-world results, such as presidential elections and sports betting results.": "分散型予測市場（AugurとGnosisなど）は人々の知恵を使って現実世界の結果を予測する、例えば大統領選挙や宝くじの結果など",
