      "Application Scenario": "アプリケーションシナリオ",
      "In the Finance Bureau of the Ares network, treasury funds come from part of the transaction fees, the punishment of malicious nodes, and pledges' inflation. Treasury funds are used to reward challengers, make up for data demanders' loss, and ecological construction.": "Aresの資金源は、一部の手数料や悪意あるノードへの処罰などから生まれる。国庫資金は、挑戦者への奨励金やエコロジー構築などに補う",
